description: All UI text must be loaded via i18n using getTranslation
alwaysApply: true
---

All UI text must be internationalized:
- Page titles
- Headings
- Button labels
- Form field labels
- Error messages
- Success messages
- Navigation text
- Static text content

Use getTranslation() method instead of hardcoded strings:
- Never use static or hardcoded text in UI components
- All text must be loaded from i18n message bundles
- Support multiple languages through proper i18n implementation
